item.title: Lacrosse continue season unbeaten
item.author: Sophie Bolton,
item.description: Finishing top of the league with a goal difference of 199, the undefeated Imperial Ladies Lacrosse 1st team are having a phenomenal season. This is the first time that we have won the league undefeated. Our season finished with a 22-2 victory over Royal Holloway in an intense and aggressive match. â€¦
